NAME

    tweethour.pl - tweets the hour like a church clock

USAGE

        perl tweethour.pl mytwittername mytwitterpassword

    or

        perl tweethour.pl mytwittername mytwitterpassword BLING

    tweethour will DONG like a church clock by default. If you provide the
    third command line argument "BLING", it will BLING instead of DONG.

PREREQUISITES

    perl
    Net::Twitter::Lite

